{% comment %}
  ONE9 Luxury Streetwear - About Page Section
{% endcomment %}

<div class="main-about section-{{ section.id }}" style="background-color: #050505; color: #ffffff; padding: 60px 0;">
  <div class="page-width">
    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 60px auto;">
      <span style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #f4c430; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;">OUR HERITAGE</span>
      <h1 style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px); font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 12px 0 20px 0; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 1px;">
        WEAR YOUR UNIVERSE
      </h1>
      <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.7; color: #b0b0b0;">
        ONE9 was born out of a vision to bridge luxury craftsmanship with raw streetwear culture. Engineered for durability, designed for movement, and tailored for those who forge their own path.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3 Pillar Cards: Story, Mission, Vision -->
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 80px;">
      <div class="glass-panel" style="padding: 36px 28px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;">
          01. THE STORY
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #d0d0d0;">
          Founded in 2024, ONE9 started with a single goal: to dismantle overpriced luxury streetwear and re-engineer it from the fabric up using heavyweight French terry cotton and precision hardware.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-panel" style="padding: 36px 28px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;">
          02. OUR MISSION
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #d0d0d0;">
          To empower individuals across the globe to express their individuality without compromising on comfort, durability, or authentic streetwear aesthetics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-panel" style="padding: 36px 28px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;">
          03. THE VISION
        </div>
        <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #d0d0d0;">
          Building an international streetwear universe with limited-edition capsule drops, sustainable manufacturing processes, and unyielding design standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: #ffffff;">
        MILESTONES & TIMELINE
      </h2>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; position: relative; padding-left: 24px; border-left: 2px solid rgba(244,196,48,0.4);">
        <div style="position: relative;">
          <div style="position: absolute; left: -31px; top: 4px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f4c430;"></div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430;">2024 • THE BEGINNING</div>
          <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #b0b0b0; margin-top: 4px;">Launch of ONE9 flagship streetwear collection with 3 iconic heavy tees.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="position: relative;">
          <div style="position: absolute; left: -31px; top: 4px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f4c430;"></div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430;">2025 • ZODIAC CAPSULE</div>
          <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #b0b0b0; margin-top: 4px;">Expanded into zodiac-inspired streetwear, footwear, and oversized hoodies.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="position: relative;">
          <div style="position: absolute; left: -31px; top: 4px; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f4c430;"></div>
          <div style="font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; color: #f4c430;">2026 • GLOBAL EXPANSION</div>
          <p style="font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #b0b0b0; margin-top: 4px;">Shipping worldwide to over 40+ countries with express priority dispatch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About ONE9",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "About ONE9"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
